data.text:
Distribution

For wholesale or consignments orders, please contact orders@wendyssubway.com.

Selected titles are distributed in Europe and the UK by Antenne Books.

Selected titles are also available for free to public libraries, schools, and prisons nationwide through the Art Resources Transfer (A.R.T.) Library Program.
